comments: Olynyk (MIA) establishes himself in a screening position in Harrell's (LAC) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Harkless (LAC) maintains a legal guarding position and absorbs the contact from Adebayo (MIA) at the end of the drive.
Harrell (LAC) makes marginal contact to Olynyk's (MIA) body after the release of his shot at the basket.
Harkless (LAC) makes contact to Olynyk's (MIA) body at the end of his drive that affects his SQBR.
Waiters (MIA) makes marginal contact to Leonard's (LAC) arm after the release on his jump shot attempt.
Adebayo (MIA) fumbles the ball as he attempts to gather.  He then gathers the ball and legally starts his dribble.

Harrell (LAC) does not beat Adebayo (MIA) to the spot and makes contact to Adebayo's body at the end of his drive. 
 The contact occurs before he is able to control the ball on his gather.

Waiters (MIA) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Williams (LAC) and cleanly blocks the shot. Following the block, Waiters makes clean ball contact to temporarily dislodge the ball from Williams after he regains control of the ball.
Waiters (MIA) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Williams (LAC) and cleanly blocks the shot.
Waiters (MIA) makes marginal contact to Leonard's (LAC) arm at the start of the drive and Leonard briefly grasps Waiters' arm as he disengages.
Patterson (LAC) and Adebayo (MIA) briefly engage and separate off-ball before the inbounds pass.
Waiters (MIA) makes contact to Leonard's (LAC) body during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Adebayo (MIA) does not get his hand under the ball and bring it to a pause as he fakes the dribble hand off.
Robinson (MIA) makes marginal contact to Leonard's (MIA) chest, but the contact does not disrupt his dribble.
Waiters (MIA) commits a take foul on Leonard (LAC).
Waiters (MIA) slightly extends his leg during his shooting motion on the jump shot attempt, but the contact with Leonard (LAC) is marginal.
